Package: EBEx
Title: An Ensemble-Based Explainable Framework for Gene Calling in Heterogeneous Diseases
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Iria", "Pose Lagoa", , "iria.poselagoa@bsc.es", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: EBEx is a R package that integrates an Ensemble-Based Explainable AI pipeline for prioritising disease relevant genes from transcriptomic data, using Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD) as a use case.
